{"tid":1663331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不要說「人多就安全」，試著說「人多加準時就安全」","createTime":"2019-10-19T10:51:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T03:01:30.000Z","uid":192517,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b25363ff2afab82e4fc53249fb341e6375a32b62","tid":1663331,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:51:15.000Z","msg":"人多當然係一個好重要既因素<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過宜家啲狗既策略係事前喺集合點周圍重狗咬人，意圖阻止市民集結<br />\n所以我哋係要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同時</span></span>多人先得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以記得<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">準時</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再遲到啦！！！！！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e4bb8242057200695d64157cadffe619d459b0","tid":1663331,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:52:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「文宣升級」巴士流動大字報<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1662724\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1662724</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wj3z6Ov.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwj3z6Ov.jpg&h=9f735918&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1ad48537a64910027b72811fafba19020efae975","tid":1663331,"uid":165510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:53:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https: