":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:39:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f933dd05db951fb0b6f5951d8c8ca7b0aee4e7d5","tid":1663331,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:58:34.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n<br />\n[i]<strong>醫療、教育方向</strong>[i]<br />\n<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"827d77d0e9e6160c0855678309d316b73d392be9","tid":1663331,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:03:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2cf5cf6dbb7158700f24879a0e673dbb2ce63c","tid":1663331,"uid":127862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:04:43.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"398a39b02e6a15d2564364615e730cd251a20808","tid":1663331,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:09:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d3e8c1424dcfd5b61ade3a8601c0b726674cd16","tid":1663331,"uid":258421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:10:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/4d/Kowloon_central1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F4%2F4d%2FKowloon_central1.jpg&h=12b6a627&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBtw 手足唔好裝修郵局 港英時期嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ad098ccb3fd38b0afb934616a8db8d19ef6077","tid":1663331,"uid":284671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:17:08.000Z","msg":"人多準時先安全！"},{"pid":"07e7c2a51848fafc53ed4f4607b25f7094fe585d","tid":1663331,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T14:48:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c1c957c61df1e7d6bbeab2e56e8a9eec00427de","tid":1663331,"uid":3002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T14:51:49.000Z","msg":"而家準時都唔夠，啲狗12點1點就佈晒周圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n推"},{"pid":"0a71317875b86426f642fe165fb838db3d80fe5e","tid":1663331,"uid":209865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T15:00:27.000Z","msg":"人多有咩用<br />\n反抗就安全"},{"pid":"9caf01bd70b1e60cef854c69b0bcfde9518407d1","tid":1663331,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:01:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}